  <entry>
    <title>MMD 靜畫 | 每月 23 文之日（2023.01）</title>
    <link href="https://copy-alcide.github.io/MMDPic/2023/MMDPic-20230123/"/>
    <id>https://copy-alcide.github.io/MMDPic/2023/MMDPic-20230123/</id>
    <published>2023-01-22T16:32:15.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-02-11T12:06:28.328Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/MMDPic-2023/Aya_20230123.png&default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/MMDPic-2023/Aya_20230123.png"></p><p>簡單的鐵道阿文圖。</p><p>不知道因爲什麼 ikbokeh 在這張圖上罷工了，於是嘗試了一種徹底不同的渲染風格。</p><p>遠景因爲場景問題很是空曠，最後手動栽了十幾棵樹。 </p><span id="more"></span><figure class="highlight plaintext"><figcaption><span>Text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">借物表</span><br><span class="line">模型：</span><br><span class="line">宝改 MikuMikuDance用　東方Project　射命丸文改変モデル</span><br><span class="line">てんぽく MMD鉄道モデル「北海道乗降場各種」</span><br><span class="line">キサノキ式キハ22</span><br><span class="line">asado ヒサカキセット</span><br><span class="line">Oyama 低木1</span><br><span class="line">渲染：</span><br><span class="line">Rui Ray-MMD</span><br><span class="line">極北P dPostPointLight_v1.00</span><br><span class="line">ikeno 不透明水彩風にするエフェクト</span><br><span class="line">そぼろ MikuMikuEffect用ディフュージョンフィルタ</span><br><span class="line">RedialC Toon_RC</span><br><span class="line">世界最弱のサーモントラウト RayMMD用のマテリアル24種類</span><br><span class="line">軟件：</span><br><span class="line">MMM ver 1.2.9.2</span><br><span class="line">MMD ver 9.26</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://wsrv.nl/?url=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/MMDPic-2023/Aya_20230123.png&amp;default=https://copy-alcide.github.io/post-images/MMDPic-2023/Aya_20230123.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;簡單的鐵道阿文圖。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不知道因爲什麼 ikbokeh 在這張圖上罷工了，於是嘗試了一種徹底不同的渲染風格。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;遠景因爲場景問題很是空曠，最後手動栽了十幾棵樹。 &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
